{"tid":2195656,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"三口家打甩限聚令告票","createTime":"2020-09-09T10:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T11:32:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"18e5852fece6cd69cdc78fb74234a14bcdf3b321","tid":2195656,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:15:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/W6TVBK7NZBFHLE6VVV2G4BBSM4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FW6TVBK7NZBFHLE6VVV2G4BBSM4%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwgw6WLWD%2BvnO7xCw116w%2BR6c%3D&h=d088a361\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FW6TVBK7NZBFHLE6VVV2G4BBSM4%2F&h=aa69c173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/W6TVBK7NZBFHLE6VVV2G4BBSM4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n三口家打甩限聚令告票<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SqKS4xOoTiEPK94-WKmt1mmoWR0=/1254x825/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HPLSD4MFIVAYND556YUV76CNLY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSqKS4xOoTiEPK94-WKmt1mmoWR0%3D%2F1254x825%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHPLSD4MFIVAYND556YUV76CNLY.png&h=4a1b8ac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■趙家賢昨晚在社交網站專頁透露，近日獲事主告知，警方決定撤銷對一家三口無理檢控。趙家賢fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特區政府實施「限聚令」後，多次出現警方以濫發告票打壓市民。東區區議員趙家賢昨透露，今年母親節當天，警方以有人違反限聚令為由進入太古城中心商場，其間有一家三口被指控違反當時上限八人「限聚令」，他隨後協助事主草擬抗辯信要求撤控，近日終獲悉抗辯成功，警方決定撤銷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n趙家賢助草擬抗辯信<br />\n<br />\n事發於5月10日，多區商場有人舉行「母親節和你Sing」抗爭活動，其中在太古城中心商場，防暴警兩度進入以膠帶拉起封鎖線，並向四名市民發出告票，指控他們違反限聚令，包括因慶祝母親節而逛商場的一家三口，連同另一中年男子。<br />\n<br />\n翻查當日報道，有人曾即場抗辯，質疑「三個人點違反限聚令？」但警員未有理會，只回應：「你同法官講」。<br />\n<br />\n事隔近四個月，當區區議員趙家賢昨晚在社交網站專頁透露，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n據限聚令法律程序，被票控人士可在21日內繳付罰款2000元，。。。。。"},{"pid":"a3a3908ee4055d9348bffaed8c1dcae409977e33","tid":2195656,"uid":346701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:21:51.000Z","msg":"呢單點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gE3n3WP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgE3n3WP.jpg&h=bdc80c01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aece706d4fa5d0ce47dfdad74adad184f55d776e","tid":2195656,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:21:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"></span>"},{"pid":"3a7e71143db445f020c8a134793346b798144407","tid":2195656,"uid":39710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:25:51.000Z","msg":"根本鳩派啦, 乜鳩都話留返俾法官講"},{"pid":"6e1dc8cae8c7c284a4d12f0e095d4b18be9475aa","tid":2195656,"uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2030e71e8c54f12f0e79c7902f21aafb0e047151","tid":2195656,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:29:14.000Z","msg":"要你搞一大輪已經係消耗緊時間成本同抗爭體力"},{"pid":"ab600e2f7128f6773af257129118ba07ba641dde","tid":2195656,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:29:37.000Z","msg":"麻煩你麻煩你"},{"pid":"70b66e18dbdbd6f3327aab48497daa4e08f9f2ca","tid":2195656,"uid":39544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a7e71143db445f020c8a134793346b798144407","tid":2195656,"uid":39710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:25:51.000Z","msg":"根本鳩派啦, 乜鳩都話留返俾法官講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:31:58.000Z","msg":"佢哋真係無成本 點解唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鳩派完就走 收票嗰個又要排期上庭諗抗辯 時間，精神都蝕晒俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f867f1be49ec1a237583eb2e17cda654831277a","tid":2195656,"uid":235853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3a3908ee4055d9348bffaed8c1dcae409977e33","tid":2195656,"uid":346701,